title: Deposit Interest Rate in Tunisia
description: Deposit Interest Rate in Tunisia was at 8.05 percent on Thursday November 10. Deposit Interest Rate in Tunisia averaged 6.06 percent from 2011 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 10.10 percent in November of 2019 and a record low of 3.68 percent in May of 2012. The Deposit Interest Rate is the average rate paid by commercial banks to individuals or corporations on deposits. This page includes a chart with historical data for Deposit Interest Rate in Tunisia.
author: World Bank
